page.title: 19About ourselves (2)
page.content: Paul likes sports, T.V. fish, and going shooting and fishing with his Dad; he collects keys. Helen K has been riding since she was three and has won a lot of prizes with her pony Dominic. Helen A's hobbies are roller skating and Drama; she also likes finding out about ghosts and going to museums and Art Galleries. Adam likes playing on his bike, watching T.V., Pool, Tennis and Badminton; he collects old money and new stamps. Donna likes swimming and going to the sea side at Felixstowe. Gabrielle has only just joined us from another school, so she hasn't worked on the Domesday Project; she likes playing with Sindy dolls and her little sister. Mr Tallack likes the Arts, travelling, walking in sparsely populated areas and convivial evenings with good friends.
